{
  "stem": "22892.4",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "If I were hit by a bomb, wouldn't-- that would be OK because-- but just to wait to be killed by all these Ukrainians, whether they're going to torture me and do that-- I've seen what they've done to a-- to a family.",
      "word_count": 43
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I was-- I was in the attic when they did it next door.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They, they wouldn't even use bullets.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They used bayonets.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "The whole family, they, they, they killed them.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They butchered them.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I mean, these were just worse than animals.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "They just had no regards of human lives.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "They just-- so I think the fear-- how I'm going to die-- catching me and all this.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I don't know what it was, really.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] I guess, maybe the will for survival-- that I wasn't even aware of it.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "It was so great.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "It was so great.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And things happened.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And sometime, I think about it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "It was almost humanly impossible to survive like I did.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "I found out later on I was the only kid that survived.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "I was the only youngster who survived from my little shtetl.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "There was no one.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "I mean, these two men were never in my shtetl.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "Like, this Moishe, I mean, came from my home.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "But he was never-- he lived somewhere else.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "So [SIGHS] I, I, I-- sometime, I don't understand that.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And right-- well, that winter, [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] one night, we found out that the Russians came through.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "The Russians were, you know, going towards west, marching.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "They came through the village.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And I thought, boy, we were liberated.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "But then they were gone.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And the same thing starts.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "So we don't know.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "We didn't know what to do.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "We were in hiding.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "We were scared to, to come out.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
